{"tid":1188372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逃犯條例下周三恢復二讀 5名民主派留守會議廳","createTime":"2019-06-06T08:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T08:16:48.000Z","uid":142903,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"75696cb9ac3473ec2b57e7f4e61a58f10a191062","tid":1188372,"uid":142903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:15:58.000Z","msg":"（獨媒特約報導）立法會下星期三將恢復二讀《逃犯條例》修訂草案，5名民主派議員在今日大會會議完結後留守會議廳，包括公民黨譚文豪、民主黨鄺俊宇、許智峯、議會陣線朱凱廸、區諾軒和范國威。他們攜同寫有「反送中」、「916上街」的示威標語在會議室內工作及聊天。會議廳內有三名保安，坐在一旁未有行動。<br />\n<br />\n立法會行政管理委員會在下午4時召開緊急特別會議，討論有關議員在會議完結後，拒絕離開會議廳的事宜。立法會主席梁君彥進入會議室前參與行管會會議前，未有回答記者提問。譚文豪亦離開會議廳，參與行管會會議。<br />\n<br />\n立法會明顯加強保安，有多名保安守在記者攝影房的通道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1064548?fbclid=IwAR2qZFbnESle8oHNDrG2eESYt6ucXkawHVsTCbZz8ohgkkT6OWA2Ocz2jrQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1064548%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2qZFbnESle8oHNDrG2eESYt6ucXkawHVsTCbZz8ohgkkT6OWA2Ocz2jrQ&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2BghVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=2ab27037\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1064548%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2qZFbnESle8oHNDrG2eESYt6ucXkawHVsTCbZz8ohgkkT6OWA2Ocz2jrQ&h=52dcfd2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1064548?fbclid=IwAR2qZFbnESle8oHNDrG2eESYt6ucXkawHVsTCbZz8ohgkkT6OWA2Ocz2jrQ</a>"},{"pid":"fdbd5e5ce200b740d5b47fd76831ceb05748c8dd","tid":1188372,"uid":43309,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:16:48.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，阻你少少位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】</strong><br />\n<br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n集合地點：維園草地<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合、3時正起步<br />\n遊行路線：維園草地遊行至金鐘添美道立法會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/SNRN6c7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSNRN6c7.gif&h=5f0c0e